{"tid":2500213,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【又中】袁國師今日話30個初步有28個係假陽性，證明屍ANAN又中，就係出盡奇招令你唔好唔記得武肺，要嚇鳩死你！！！！","createTime":"2021-04-22T12:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T14:11:12.000Z","uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"511c4e5f47937f17102e1588cd3b3683920299e2","tid":2500213,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:43:26.000Z","msg":"【最新】袁國勇視察華大基因後相信，一批約三十個樣本，有一至兩個高病毒量，污染其他樣本，以致出現假陽性<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/urgentnews.jsp?taskId=21900&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Furgentnews.jsp%3FtaskId%3D21900%26refer%3DShare&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrZR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=6ea73849\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Furgentnews.jsp%3FtaskId%3D21900%26refer%3DShare&h=26b1f606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/urgentnews.jsp?taskId=21900&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個現象<br />\n睇下呢個現象屍ANAN技術總監點講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9faQkIA6YNU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9faQkIA6YNU&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrZR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=d2329461\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9faQkIA6YNU</a><br />\n<br />\n專登係右邊大字寫死亡人數<br />\n每日都要提你呢啲數字<br />\n驚你唔記得左「疫情係好撚恐佈」呢回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPhRnAdPkgLhnKCu5ut6EjoSuRpkC95XHvxXCTqjXEvZP?filename=6wjaVoM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6wjaVoM.jpg&h=175a63d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVYykjJy7pWYER53Lw2aEW2QsqiuTw17wW6fQjkNMXcdG?filename=XwQmhB6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwQmhB6.jpg&h=cb03e30c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n死亡數字越高越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUhpDicf6xjmLwctBgLh5QxaAKADCxYEaJj8VEz5rFuoZ?filename=SDu2Mvr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSDu2Mvr.jpg&h=b9870538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n數字越高，我地帶出既論點【防疫措施】就越多人BUY<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeUcTwkdvVrpgGYLxmad9AtU8NeryCbC11NiDeW1N95JQ?filename=G75YjQr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG75YjQr.jpg&h=c920f74a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恐懼可以帶起收視<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbAPy2HpPn7Sp2UFkBRePYsTHYNYYJsfq21836FWnT3Fc?filename=Z24qKg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ24qKg6.jpg&h=f2de3732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n恐懼會KEEP住令你日日睇我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ3jQfUm9a86NSqPsJbDHS4cUK1EVJvRh8qX1ypnWYN6D?filename=CZ9qKg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZ9qKg6.jpg&h=f065fcc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n流得越多血，收視越高／防疫論點越多人BUY<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXfcupx3uJDfzEo6s6GBWxi5DdHLksdbjsWT9MwdYXrHV?filename=UOvYjQs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUOvYjQs.jpg&h=255cc5fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無人將我上面既野講出口，不過其實係好明顯既心理現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQAYvJQAaYyDemibMppTVffZiKhQJAxWXGrTHHWGvx8Hq?filename=aPS4foM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPS4foM.jpg&h=730bb0ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">If it bleeds, it leads<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n​<br />\n死得人多，就可以make our point better (我地講既野越有說服力，例如防疫措施)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最重要講左佢地點解唔報康復人數<br />\n因為康復人數唔會令到你地驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZdP5MnzbpjYx4GRzHmSpKqE7xHRy47Ksm4dwJKqxMVTY?filename=j5y7daM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5y7daM.jpg&h=883cbc7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmcs3jx8gW1b2HVaaBVC6ko6HaEr8B28ykokodzte1Q5V4?filename=wbQYjQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwbQYjQM.jpg&h=01ea213a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP3EirM3pbKDJFkYU5mXaYX8RV1HqoSXjXGEAMNzDuiym?filename=WxOGhDu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxOGhDu.jpg&h=eff5d7fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP3EirM3pbKDJFkYU5mXaYX8RV1HqoSXjXGEAMNzDuiym?filename=WxOGhDu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxOGhDu.jpg&h=eff5d7fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP3EirM3pbKDJFkYU5mXaYX8RV1HqoSXjXGEAMNzDuiym?filename=WxOGhDu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxOGhDu.jpg&h=eff5d7fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n​<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇返香港<br />\n<br />\n老蕭每日都會報全球確診數字嚇鳩死你班老野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfJotXdozGf4ja5edFP2PqotmZUofiS1H16vvKt3gtcaM?filename=9qPRERW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9qPRERW.jpg&h=5021cb0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYmm7mxPyhUc4TPKDRpo98pTdGv4YwEk8dS6fZ4VQRcsW?filename=uorkybV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuorkybV.jpg&h=42f595bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVxTpDgiMKTTYggbtzFRxYg7MbZ2GkWSHm9a5m1qDaYBh?filename=2Ks4fqf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Ks4fqf.jpg&h=a3807bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報四日頭條有三日係講病毒「殺」到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPDwamhwBFtusuAaBozoF82znYCXo2S9bydJCzhui9suo?filename=eyUrpJm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeyUrpJm.jpg&h=942c5cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRKmVvBdGs8X7CcJXXKJcCHayr2QcaTkPtbTrmRNywxmF?filename=Lnhc4Jm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLnhc4Jm.jpg&h=4cc5f094&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVzYpYvsD4uJwiUUywNhAQfkQaaZvNTtFPeSuotRrt4Gk?filename=NcS1dBE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNcS1dBE.jpg&h=87b1ff1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n殖入式嚇鳩你有武肺就「人心惶惶驚到震」<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmakf8PxkTc61tKKPLNKizEEAxXcqvmHJY6DhgubxdKWfv?filename=p5sWQYT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp5sWQYT.png&h=83002d7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong